  "description": "A sheaf is a [presheaf](./presheaf.md) — an assignment of data to each object of a [site](../../higher-topos-theory/terms/site.md) — that satisfies the [sheaf condition](../../higher-topos-theory/terms/sheaf-condition.md): compatible local data can be uniquely glued into global data.",
